{"tid":1862444,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［請廣傳］黃店賣淘寶貨比銀髮食人血鏝頭","createTime":"2020-02-04T15:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T17:24:09.000Z","uid":335157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"96cea3d25822f24b18af299c8ce48acb0d182161","tid":1862444,"uid":335157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSkyhab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSkyhab.png&h=19ec54f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">笑咗 以為自己係醫學專家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係高科技公司<br />\n條片仲要係同支那一模一樣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6g1JEoJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6g1JEoJ.png&h=f0c80876&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9OoEoK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9OoEoK.png&h=adab3abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你部機究竟通過咗邊個歐盟認證？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定強國淘寶認證<br />\n拎個認證嚟睇睇<br />\n啲銀髮買咗部機 唔戴口罩真係多得你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXwYtho.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXwYtho.png&h=835d4da2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EvVZcJ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvVZcJ4.png&h=ce949722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前果啲乜乜降噪3.0 <br />\n已經令人懷疑你究竟係乜撚嘢科技大廠<br />\n做到人地Bose嘅效果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQfROhR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQfROhR.png&h=3b0fe50a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KSyPzXW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKSyPzXW.png&h=24bd41c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2m4vjpF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2m4vjpF.png&h=f3688f32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGPnUX4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGPnUX4.png&h=e1e30cbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n扮黃店罷工 你老母全間舖都係支那貨<br />\n淘寶 search 中國水站 <br />\n就會搵到 佢果部空氣清新機同耳機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nUNs55k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnUNs55k.png&h=a2afc21d&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好多人以為係HK品牌</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"35d924aacfbe481d9c7ba69b8ef0dabc30bd8244","tid":1862444,"uid":335157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"純粹驚人戴咗佢部機出街<br />\n以為唔洗戴口罩<br />\n日本機可能仲有少少用淘寶出品 <br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6f44a40c822c20ff50ce56d02a7a13d3ba3c7c","tid":1862444,"uid":168567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:31:16.000Z","msg":"咁多殘體"},{"pid":"79b800da543aef8d5939a504cd87c7ccc1347ecd","tid":1862444,"uid":335157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f6f44a40c822c20ff50ce56d02a7a13d3ba3c7c","tid":1862444,"uid":168567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:31:16.000Z","msg":"咁多殘體"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:32:10.000Z","msg":"殘體係佢個供應商嘅post"},{"pid":"50b20937e72ad96d9d0730adc354c0d566153d82","tid":1862444,"uid":104961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}